parameters:
\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[yurisu_trouble]\AA[2]Yurika: "That was close. I never expected that our teachers
and seniors would turn against us..."

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[yurisu_trouble]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Thank you for saving me... If I were alone... I
would have been captured..."

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "The trap here has been activated. They won't be
able to approach us for a while."

\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Ugh... This is a desperate situation, isn't
it..."

\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Don't be so pessimistic. You and I are still here.
When it comes to our feelings for Akane, we won't lose to
anyone."

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "The president loves Akane that much... I thought
you were at odds with each other..."

\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[yurisu_trouble]\AA[2]Yurika: "I was unconsciously aware of it. That's why it
showed in my attitude... Laugh at my foolishness."

\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[yurisu_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "You rest here for a while. I'll go activate the
remaining traps."

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[yurisu_angry]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "I'll go with you! It's better to be together...
than alone!"

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Are you worried about me? You're kind. But don't
worry. I won't betray you again. After all, we love the same
person."
\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[yurisu_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "Then let's go. Let's take back our Akane."

\F[furi_smile]Akane: "Nadeshiko... I've found you!! I won't let you
escape!!"

\FF[nakosu_trouble]Nadeshiko: "!! Even if I fall... as long as the president is
here...!"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[nakosu_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "Nadeshiko!! I will now free you from the chains that
bind you...!!"

\FF[yurisu_angry]Yurika: "I was careless after all!! I thought if I stayed by
Nadeshiko's side, this chance would come!!"
\F[furi_angry]Akane: "Guhhh...! Such a thing won't stop me!!"

\FF[yurisu_trouble]Yurika: "No way... The power that defeated me...! Gah...!!
Run away!! Nadeshiko-san!!"

\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[yurisu_trouble]\AA[2]Yurika: "You are our last hope!! I'll hold them off
here...!"

\F[furi_smile]Akane: "As expected, the president is smart..! And she
learns well from her own experiences... She's gotten closer
to me than anyone else!"

\F[furi_smile]Akane: "And... even a Poison Burst! That's why! With you
here, there's no way Nadeshiko can escape anymore!!"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[yurisu_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "Me... surrender? The one I love isn't the you of
now. That's right. Someone more free..."

\F[furi_smile]\FF[yurisu_shadow]\AA[2]Yurika: "Yes... Even if it means running through the
hallways... I don't mind... Such unrestrained freedom... I
admire it... Freedom is wonderful"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[yurisu_shadow]\AA[1]Akane: "Why doesn't the president become like that too?
There's no need to be stubborn. Don't you like me? Being
with me would be nothing but a reward♪"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[yurisu_shadow]\AA[2]Yurika: "With Akane...? Is, is that even allowed?! It, it
certainly is a reward! The happiest gift of all♪"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[yuri_free]\AA[1]Akane: "Now, all that's left is to leave Nadeshiko alone...
You'll help me, right?"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[yuri_free]\AA[2]Yurika: "...Of course. If we can bring her down, then I'll
be released from everything♪ To become truly free! I
wouldn't miss such a reward for the world♪"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[yuri_free]\AA[2]Yurika: "Yes. But I think this would be better. There's one
trap that hasn't been activated yet. If Nadeshiko goes
there..."
\F[furi_smile]\FF[yuri_free]\AA[1]Akane: "I see♪ As expected, the president is useful♪"

\F[furi_smile]\FF[yuri_free]\AA[2]Yurika: "I'm not the president anymore, though, am I?♪ Thank
you!! Ahhnn♪ For my master's praise... I can do anything♪
Any dirty thing at all♪"
